  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "For output 1 following will be the inputs:\r\n\r\n1. Formulation of a draft Regional GAP Scheme for SAARC countries – covering technical criteria, certification body criteria and certification process,  accreditation criteria and process\r\n\r\n2. Regional Consultation workshop (2 representatives - each country) to agree on finalized draft\r\n\r\n3. 4 National Workshops – one in each country\r\n\r\n4. Regional workshop for sharing country experience on the GAP Scheme  formulated and reporting and finalising of regional GAP scheme\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nFor Output 2 following are the four inputs:\r\n\r\n1. Setting up of Steering Committee to steer the process\r\n\r\n 2. Setting up of Technical Committee to develop the National Interpretation of the regional GAP technical standard \r\n\r\n 3. Meeting of TC to finalize the National interpretation of GAP standard \r\n\r\n4. Study tour for Scheme Owners (See Output 3 Activity 4)"
    },
    "ne": null
  },
